        "description": "<p><em>Universe Sandbox</em> is a conversion of the <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/80592/universe-sandbox/\">PC game of the same name</a> to an augmented reality format. Like the original version of <em>Universe Sandbox</em>, this version also presents itself as a realistic simulation of the universe and puts the player in complete control of its stars, planets and moons. The player can customize the mass, density, motion, composition, climate, and appearance of planets and watch how the changes affect the planet's relationship with its celestial neighbors\u2014or, if they want a more extreme result, they can just fling them into other objects and watch them collide. The player can also change the temperature of the sun and create supermassive black holes to cause further destruction.</p>",
